{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"說情者的說情，將無益於他們。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"他們怎麼退避這教訓呢？"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"他們好像一群驚慌的驢子，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":51,"Text":"剛逃避了一隻獅子一樣。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":52,"Text":"不然，他們中的每個人都希望獲得一些展開的天經。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":53,"Text":"絕不然，他們不畏懼後世！"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":54,"Text":"真的，這《古蘭經》確是一個教誨！"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":55,"Text":"誰願意，誰記憶它，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":56,"Text":"他們只因真主的意欲而記憶它。他是應受敬畏的，他是宜於赦宥的。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"我以復活日盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"我以自責的靈魂盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"難道人猜想我絕不能集合他的骸骨嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"不然，（我將集合他的骸骨），而且能使他的每個手指復原。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"不然，人欲長此放蕩下去。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他問復活日在甚麼時候。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"當眼目昏花，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"月亮昏暗，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"日月相合的時候，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"在那日，人將說：「逃到哪裡去呢？」"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"絕不然，絕無任何避難所。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"在那日，唯你的主那裡，有安定之所。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"在那日，各人將被告知自己前前後後做過的事情。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"不然，各人對自己就是明証，"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"即使他多方托辭。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"你不要搖動你的舌頭，以便你倉卒地誦讀它。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"集合它和誦讀它，確是我的責任。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"當我誦讀它的時候，你當靜聽我的誦讀。"},{"SurahNumber":75,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"然後解釋它，也是我的責任。"}]}